<HEAD>Mother of Iran's Khamenei Dies Day He Confirmed in Post</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Hajieh Mirdamadi, the mother of Iran's
new leader Ali Khamenei, died the day her son was confirmed as
Ayatollah Ruhollah Khomeini's successor, the Islamic Republic News
Agency reported today.
   Ms. Mirdamadi died Sunday of heart failure, IRNA said. She was
