Gaza Strip, territories occupied by Israel.
   The news agency said Hussein reaffirmed the Palestinian people's
right to self-determination ``on their national soil.''
   It also said the king reiterated that no settlement could be
reached without the Palestine Liberation Organization, which Israel
considers a terrorist group.
